body:
You need to change vite.config.ts ```server: {
    proxy: {
      '/dolphinscheduler': {
        target: loadEnv('development', './').VITE_APP_DEV_WEB_URL,
        changeOrigin: true
      }
    }
  }``` to ```server: {
    proxy: {
      '/dolphinscheduler/': {
        target: loadEnv('development', './').VITE_APP_DEV_WEB_URL,
        changeOrigin: true
      }
    }
  }```. add `/` after `/dolphinscheduler`
